  COMMON WORKFLOW:
    1. Write code
    2. Right Cmd + R           → See if it works
    3. Not working? Right Cmd + D → Debug it
    4. Want to test snippet? Highlight → Right Cmd + C
    5. Before commit: Right Cmd + T → Run all tests


